PN,43601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,FA woman from Cornwall who was unable
OL,7,Fto see following the birth of her
OL,8,Ffirst child has had her sight restored
OL,9,Ffollowing a plasma donation.
OL,11,FJessica Kent-Hazledine said she feared
OL,12,F"the worst" when her vision started to
OL,13,Fgo in April last year, but a year on
OL,14,Fher sight is "so much better".
OL,16,FThe 33-year-old dentist woke up two
OL,17,Fweeks after having her son with little
OL,18,Fvision in her left eye, which she put
OL,19,Fdown to tiredness.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@KO]vD@NOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
