OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,FHowever, she soon lost vision in her
OL,7,Fright eye, leaving her "terrified"
OL,8,Fthat she would not see her baby grow
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,F"I was a new mum, not getting much
OL,12,Fsleep," Ms Kent-Hazledine said.
OL,14,F"But I thought I should probably get
OL,15,Fit checked out and the next thing I
OL,16,Fknew I was having an urgent MRI and
OL,17,Fblood tests. It was all very scary, I
OL,18,Fwas thinking the worst.
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@bO]sD@AOUtD@GO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,F"When my vision went in my right eye,
OL,7,Ftoo, I was terrified ` I thought I
OL,8,Fwouldn't be able to see my baby grow
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,F"I wouldn't be able to see how his
OL,12,Fface changed or when he took his first
OL,13,Fsteps or had his first day at school.
OL,15,F"I had been a mum for two weeks and
OL,16,Fwas faced with the prospect of not
OL,17,Fbeing able to see my son again, it was
OL,18,Fawful."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,FAfter trying some other treatments,
OL,7,Fmedics arranged a plasma exchange for
OL,8,FMs Kent-Hazledine which was carried
OL,9,Fout by a new service run by NHS Blood
OL,10,Fand Transplant (NHSBT) in the South
OL,11,FWest.
OL,13,FAs part of the process, a patient's
OL,14,Fplasma ` the liquid component of blood
OL,15,Fthat helps transport blood cells,
OL,16,Fnutrients and hormones around the body
OL,17,F` is removed from the bloodstream and
OL,18,Freplaced with donor plasma.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,FThis helped stop the antibodies in Ms
OL,7,FKent-Hazledine's blood from attacking
OL,8,Fand damaging the protective layer
OL,9,Faround the nerve fibres in her eyes.
OL,11,FMs Kent-Hazledine described the
OL,12,Ftreatment as "so simple".
OL,14,FShe had five exchanges at Royal
OL,15,FCornwall Hospital and things started
OL,16,Fto improve by the third.
OL,18,FMs Kent-Hazledine can now see clearly
OL,19,Fout of her right eye and has around
OL,20,F75% sight in her left.
OL,26,@tD@NOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,F"By the fifth (exchange), I felt
OL,7,Fpretty much back to myself, it felt
OL,8,Flike magic," she added.
OL,10,F"It's been almost a year now and my
OL,11,Fsight is so much better ` I still have
OL,12,Fsome blurring in half of my left eye
OL,13,Fbut I can look after my son and live
OL,14,Fan independent life, which I was
OL,15,Fworried I wouldn't be able to."
OL,17,FThe plasma exchange was performed by
OL,18,FNHSBT's therapeutic apheresis services
OL,19,F(TAS), which is working with four
OL,20,Fhospitals in the region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]rD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,FMs Kent-Hazledine was the first person
OL,7,Fin Cornwall to use the service.
OL,9,FShe said: "I feel so lucky that it was
OL,10,Farriving in the area just as I needed
OL,11,Fit ` it was amazing and I'm glad that
OL,12,Fother people will get to benefit, too."
OL,14,FShe added: "I'm eternally grateful to
OL,15,Fthose people who donated blood and
OL,16,Fplasma ` it's only thanks to them that
OL,17,Fthat plasma was available and I'm able
OL,18,Fto see again.
OL,26,@qD@KOUtD@gO]vD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,F"I don't think people realise just how
OL,7,Fmuch good, donation can do ` we all
OL,8,Fknow blood can be used in emergencies
OL,9,Fbut it can also be used to help so
OL,10,Fmany people like me.
OL,12,F"I'd urge absolutely everybody who is
OL,13,Feligible to go and give blood or
OL,14,Fplasma ` and thank you to those who
OL,15,Falready do."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,FEmma Warner, lead nurse at NHS Blood
OL,7,Fand Transplant's TAS in Plymouth, who
OL,8,Ftreated Ms Kent-Hazledine, said: "This
OL,9,Fvital service is giving patients
OL,10,Faccess to timely, specialist care
OL,11,Fclose to home.
OL,13,F"For new mum Jessica, this meant
OL,14,Feverything. She was able to receive
OL,15,Fthe treatment she needed as an
OL,16,Foutpatient, staying by her baby's side
OL,17,Finstead of enduring long, stressful
OL,18,Fjourneys or the prospect of being
OL,19,Fadmitted far from home.
OL,26,@pD@bOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,F"It makes us so happy to be able to
OL,7,Fhelp patients like Jessica but we
OL,8,Fcouldn't do what we do without the
OL,9,Fgenerosity of blood and plasma donors,
OL,10,Fand I'd like to encourage everybody
OL,11,Fwho is able to register to donate."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for NHS England's
OL,14,Fspecialised commissioning team in the
OL,15,FSouth West also welcomed the launch of
OL,16,FTAS in the region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775207141
OL,3,CWoman from Cornwall who lost vision
OL,4,Cafter giving birth has sight restored
OL,6,F"Plasma exchange is not typically
OL,7,Fcommissioned as a standalone service
OL,8,Fby NHS England, as it often sits
OL,9,Fwithin broader treatment pathways,"
OL,10,Fthey said.
OL,12,F"However, we knew there was a gap in
OL,13,Fprovision of this service in the
OL,14,Fpeninsula and, following a procurement
OL,15,Fprocess, we commissioned NHS Blood and
OL,16,FTransplant to fulfil this need."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]tD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
